{{page-toolbar pageTitle="插件" isDemo=false}}

{{#paper-content class="md-padding"}}
<div class="doc-content">
    <p>
        <code>ember-paper</code> 不包含 material design 规范标准描述的每一个组件。
    </p>
    <p>插件使得他能够可选的包含一些非常见情况下的扩展组件。</p>
    <p>注意，插件是由第三方开发人员维护的，因此他们可能不会始终保持更新。</p>
    
    {{#paper-card}}
        {{#paper-toolbar}}
            {{#paper-toolbar-tools}}
                <h2>ember-paper 插件</h2>
            {{/paper-toolbar-tools}}
        {{/paper-toolbar}}
        {{#paper-list}}
            {{#paper-subheader}}
                material design 组件
            {{/paper-subheader}}
            {{#paper-item class="md-2-line"}}
                <div class="md-list-item-text">
                    <h3>
                        <a href="https://github.com/CoachLogix/ember-paper-stepper">ember-paper-stepper</a>
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        提供 <a href="https://material.io.guidelines/components/steppers.html"> ember paper stepper </a>的一个实现
                    </p>
                </div>
            {{/paper-item}}
            {{#paper-item class="md-2-line"}}
        <div class="md-list-item-text">
          <h3><a href="https://github.com/CoachLogix/ember-paper-selection-dialog">ember-paper-selection-dialog</a></h3>
          <p>
            Provides dialogs for selections. Think of it as a select component, but using dialogs.
            提供一个选择对话框，一个选择组件，但是使用弹框的形式
          </p>
        </div>
      {{/paper-item}}

      {{#paper-item class="md-2-line"}}
        <div class="md-list-item-text">
          <h3><a href="https://github.com/CoachLogix/ember-paper-swiper">ember-paper-swiper</a></h3>
          <p>
            Implements material design's onboarding <a target="_blank" href="https://material.io/guidelines/growth-communications/onboarding.html#onboarding-top-user-benefits">Top user benefits</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      {{/paper-item}}

      {{#paper-item class="md-2-line"}}
        <div class="md-list-item-text">
          <h3><a href="https://github.com/miguelcobain/ember-paper-expansion-panel">ember-paper-expansion-panel</a></h3>
          <p>
            Provides an implementation of <a target="_blank" href="https://material.io/guidelines/components/expansion-panels.html">material expansion panels</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      {{/paper-item}}

      {{#paper-item class="md-2-line"}}
        <div class="md-list-item-text">
          <h3><a href="https://github.com/ibarrick/paper-data-table">paper-data-table</a></h3>
          <p>
            Provides an implementation of <a target="_blank" href="https://material.io/guidelines/components/data-tables.html">material data tables</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      {{/paper-item}}

      {{#paper-item class="md-2-line"}}
        <div class="md-list-item-text">
          <h3><a href="https://github.com/devotox/ember-paper-pikaday">ember-paper-pikaday</a></h3>
          <p>
          	Ember Pikaday wrapped as a Paper Item
          </p>
        </div>
      {{/paper-item}}

      {{#paper-item class="md-2-line"}}
        <div class="md-list-item-text">
          <h3><a href="https://github.com/devotox/ember-paper-time-picker">ember-paper-time-picker</a></h3>
          <p>
          	Time Picker attached to an input field that allows both keyboard and mouse entry
          </p>
        </div>
      {{/paper-item}}

      {{#paper-item class="md-2-line"}}
        <div class="md-list-item-text">
          <h3><a href="https://github.com/devotox/ember-paper-password">ember-paper-password</a></h3>
          <p>
          	Simple paper input field with type password with an eye icon on the right that when clicked toggles between showing the password and not
          </p>
        </div>
      {{/paper-item}}

      {{#paper-item class="md-2-line"}}
        <div class="md-list-item-text">
          <h3><a href="https://github.com/devotox/ember-paper-input-mask">ember-paper-input-mask</a></h3>
          <p>
            Simple paper input field that wraps around <a href="https://github.com/pzuraq/ember-inputmask">Ember Inputmask </a>
            Look to Input mask to see possible options along with Paper Input options
          </p>
        </div>
      {{/paper-item}}

      {{paper-divider}}
